1.3.0.name: de.thryrallo.vrc.avatar-performance-tools
1.3.0.description:
Calculated and evaluates some avatar metric not currently taking into account by vrchats ranking system.

Most prominently gives a breakdown over VRAM usage of different parts of the avatar.
